fields.name: AlreadyRenewedPermitMessage
fields.fieldText: You have already completed a renewal application for your permit. To see your renewal application please review the "Applications" tab at the top of the screen in the navigation bar.

fields.name: RenewalConfirmationMessage
fields.fieldText: This is confirmation that you have completed the renewal process.

fields.name: PaidOnlineMessage
fields.fieldText: You can access your receipt on the payment record found here and click the "download receipt" button.

fields.name: AMountWHSTSubtotal
fields.fieldText: {!TotalAmountWithHST}

fields.name: NoOrBlankResponseMessage
fields.fieldText:
You must be able to agree to all the declaration statements in this application in order to proceed with the online renewal of your Permit.


If you CANNOT agree with, or are uncertain of how to respond to, any of the confirmation or declaration statements, please contact the NSCP for further instruction.


Select "Previous" to go back to the previous screen and modify your answers.

Select "Finish" to exit the renewal application (your application responses will be saved).

fields.name: noteligibleforpemitmessage
fields.fieldText: You are not eligible to renew a permit at this time. Please contact NSCP for assistance

fields.name: NoRenew
fields.fieldText: You may not renew at this time. Please check your account for an outstanding balance or contact NSCP for clarification.

fields.name: MakeSureYouClickNextMessage
fields.fieldText:
Do Not Close The Page!

Please ensure you click the "Next" button once the green check mark appears.

Failure to do so may result in renewals being processed inaccurately.

fields.name: PaymentUnsuccessfulMessage
fields.fieldText: Sorry your payment was not successful please try again

fields.name: PermitDoesntExistMessage
fields.fieldText: There is no active permit associated to your registration. Please contact the NSCP for further information.
